JDBC  (Java Database Connectivity)

Java program values (variables)<------>JDBC Drivers<------->Database package

Types of JDBC Drivers
---------------------
Type 1 driver	: JDBC-ODBC bridge driver 
Type 2 driver	: Native API driver
Type 3 driver	: Network protocol driver
Type 4 driver	: Thin driver 

Type1 & Type2 drivers are Platform/OS Dependent (developed using C&C++)

Type3 driver : for Very Large database, 
 		used by Servers, Search Engines

Type 4 driver is most commonly used driver. for majority of service oriented applications

